8 participating in training programs sponsored by the Council. Every
9 law enforcement agency employing police or peace officers in this
10 state shall submit to CLEET on or before October 1 of each calendar
11 year a complete list of all commissioned employees with a current
12 mailing address and phone number for each such employee. In
13 addition to the above, CLEET may impose an administrative fine for
14 violations of this section.
15 2. A tribal law enforcement agency that has peace officers
