20 shall report the commissioning, resignation, or termination of
21 commission for any reason of a cross-deputized tribal police or
22 peace officer to CLEET within ten (10) days of the commissioning,
23 resignation, or termination. Failure to comply with the provisions
24
HB3055 HFLR Page 25
