6 discretion, certify such person providing that all
7 other statutory requirements have been met,
8 c. a verdict of guilt or entry of a plea of guilty or
9 nolo contendere or an "Alford" plea or any plea other
10 than a not guilty plea for a felony offense, a crime
11 of moral turpitude, or a crime of domestic violence,
12 d. falsification or a willful misrepresentation of
13 information in an employment application or
14 application to the Council on Law Enforcement
